sequenceDiagram
  participant Operator
  participant VBS as HMI VBScript
  participant HMI
  participant PLC
  participant Motion
  Operator->>VBS: Select CSV / Load
  VBS->>VBS: Parse complete file
  VBS-->>Operator: Reject line/schema/count error
  VBS->>HMI: Commit X/Y arrays + count
  HMI->>PLC: Request ID + data-ready
  PLC->>PLC: Validate count/range/state
  PLC-->>HMI: Accepted or error code
  Operator->>PLC: Start
  PLC->>Motion: Homing / target / speed / direction
  Motion-->>PLC: Encoder counts and sensors
  PLC-->>HMI: Index, status, alarms
